eply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Summon: Shard of the core</span><hr size=1> Where does this spell drop? I have heard it's somewhere on velious but do certain mobs drop it or what? Any information on drops for this spell would help. I like to have a complete spell book and this spell is just evading me <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=variathemage>Varia the mage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 65<br> <font color=#333333>(11/18/02 5:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1664.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Summon: Shard of the core</span><hr size=1> It drops off holgresh in Wakening Land.  They are flying monkeys.  They are always either a wizard or a mage.  There is a cave full of them, plus some roam the zone.  Best bet is to give the cave a try.  Becareful though because sometimes they path under the world and can still nuke you.  CR and FR are suggested. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=108671">Varia Darselai</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> Arch Convoker</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=belhaven>Belhaven</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 141<br> <font color=#333333>(11/18/02 8:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=htt