You can just about solo the entrance to the Holgresh cave with a 44 pet (I used water or air).  I used to sit halfway down the tunnel and pick off the occaisional wanders who exit the cave.  Keep your Fire Resist up and let pet take the agro, if they start to chain nuke you it can be nasty.  Their pets aren't a danger except that they can engage your pet.  It's a good idea to have some form of SoW potion handy cos you will have to run to Skyshrine occaisionally if you get adds.<br>
<br>
Soloing here was quite good.  Quite often you would be visited by someone doing the shackles quest who needs an uncommon drop (which I've forgotten), group with them.<br>
<br>
Shard Spell is a rare drop, I reckon about 1 in 50. <p>Chard  58 Conjurer with Healers of Norrath</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xerphanis>Xerphanis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 43<br> <font color=#333333>(11/20/02 4:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1664.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Summon: Shard of the core</span><hr size=1> I got my copy from Velks in the Upper Kobold area when Velious first came out. <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://mitglied.lycos.de/sirnamib/hpbimg/xerph.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->[65 Arch Convoker] <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=60465" target="top">Xerphanis</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Officer of &lt; <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.monkeyo.org/enshadowed" target="top">Enshadowed</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> &gt;</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showPrevMessage?topicID=1664.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showNextMessage?topicID=1664.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1664.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add